            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jun 2026 01:05:53 -0500</pubDate>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <h3>What's new in V3.2</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Fixed Desktop permission popup that kept reappearing</li>
